            modified with [1mset-mark-command [22mor [1mexchange-point-and-mark[22m.  Note that whether or not the region is active has no effect on its use within emacs style widgets, it simply determines whether it is highlighted. In vi mode,  the
            region corresponds to selected text in visual mode.

